00:27:41,236 --> 00:27:41,995
It's okay, Mom.

710
00:27:42,075 --> 00:27:43,636
I'll go get him now, okay?

711
00:27:43,716 --> 00:27:44,316
I'll go get

712
00:27:44,396 --> 00:27:46,156
